Package cdx.opencdx.classification.analyzer.service.impl

Class OpenCDXAnalysisEngineImpl

java.lang.Object
cdx.opencdx.classification.analyzer.service.impl.OpenCDXAnalysisEngineImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
OpenCDXAnalysisEngine
@Service public class OpenCDXAnalysisEngineImpl extends Object implements OpenCDXAnalysisEngine
Demonstration implementation of the OpenCDXAnalysisEngine class. This class is responsible for analyzing the patient's questionnaire and connected test data, and returning the classification response. This class can be backed by rules engines, machine learning models, or any other classification engine. This is provided to demonstrate the interface and the expected behavior.
